data.description: Remarkable home in the desirable Tartesso! Nestled on a large corner lot, this beauty offers 5 bed, 4 baths, RV gate & parking, and a 3-car garage w/extended driveway. Enter to find a formal living room and an inviting family/dining room that opens to the kitchen! The culinary space boasts granite counters & backsplash, staggered cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, and an island w/breakfast bar. Tile floors downstairs, abundant natural light, and recessed lighting enhance the welcoming vibe. Upstairs, the carpet adds comfort to the versatile loft & bedrooms w/walk-in closets! Even more surprising are the TWO main bedrooms, each featuring a full bathroom. HUGE! Back & side yards provide a covered patio, space for BBQ, play area, sizable storage shed, and much room for entertaining. Don't miss it!
